lyrics:
[Verse]
Ian, the superhero, so brave and so strong
Fights off monsters, all the night long
With a cape of power and a heart so true
He's the hero we all look up to

[Chorus]
Ian, oh Ian, our hero so grand
Saving the world with his mighty hand
He's fearless and strong, always standing tall
Ian, our superhero, he'll never let us fall
